there any

00:05:19.552 --> 00:05:20.770
tip which you would like to give,?

00:05:20.770 --> 00:05:25.020
I talk to lots of people and they are like,

00:05:25.020 --> 00:05:28.650
they always feel that will they be able to
talk on screen and

00:05:28.650 --> 00:05:32.480
will they be really able to keep up with the
audience hopes, and all.

00:05:32.480 --> 00:05:34.840
So, they get lots of anxiousness and nervousness.

00:05:34.840 --> 00:05:39.040
So, like do you have any tips for the newcomers,
like do not feel alone,

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:40.320
everybody gets nervous, and all.

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:48.690
Santosh: I mean, so from past 2 years, we
are actually just doing virtual things, right.

00:05:48.690 --> 00:05:52.580
So I would say whenever you are going virtual,
I think, uh, the thing is.

00:05:52.580 --> 00:05:54.690
you should concentrate on your content, don't
think

00:05:54.690 --> 00:05:57.310
because there is no one to actually give you
feedback, right,

00:05:57.310 --> 00:06:03.740
Especially when you are doing live streams
and, like giving a talk in a virtual

00:06:03.740 --> 00:06:04.740
conference,

00:06:04.740 --> 00:06:06.900
no one is there to actually give you feedback.
So remember,

00:06:06.900 --> 00:06:11.390
just try to be yourself and just have confidence
on yourself, that will pay.

00:06:11.390 --> 00:06:15.610
But in case you are actually presenting in
a, like, in-person conference,

00:06:15.610 --> 00:06:19.240
I think, the entire scenario changes, right.

00:06:19.240 --> 00:06:21.470
Now you have people in front of you.

00:06:21.470 --> 00:06:24.440
So try to make as much as eye contact as possible.

00:06:24.440 --> 00:06:28.600
Try to, I mean, of course not with 300 people,
but some people, right, I mean okay.

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:34.440
They are listening to you and, again, like

00:06:34.440 --> 00:06:38.760
if you have your content, don't like try to
go out of your content.

00:06:38.760 --> 00:06:40.870
Right. You know, your content really well.

00:06:40.870 --> 00:06:44.920
So sometime it happens that okay, in just
flow, we actually talk about something else,

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:48.770
which isn't related to your content, but probably
you didn't want it to mention it. Right.

00:06:48.770 --> 00:06:54.350
And then entire talk stretches up and entire
topic goes somewhere else. And everyone is

00:06:54.350 --> 00:06:55.350
confused.

00:06:55.350 --> 00:06:57.780
So try to like concentrate on what your topic is.

00:06:57.780 --> 00:07:00.300
And of course, eye contact and, be cool.

00:07:00.300 --> 00:07:04.430
