to 10 minutes.

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:17.890
So, and, uh, I think have a bottle of water
with you because you need it.

00:07:17.890 --> 00:07:22.200
Anuradha: Yeah. I mean, yeah, really, really
nice tips because

00:07:22.200 --> 00:07:26.010
